    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Support us by Wishlisting</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/c4780c718efaa856fe4a8bc6b57188fb.poster.avif?t=1708977933\" width=433 height=85 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/c4780c718efaa856fe4a8bc6b57188fb.webm?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Hello I am Brian and this is my first publicly released game, thanks for checking it out!<br><strong>Kitsune Battlemage</strong> is an intense elemental magic combat game where you're not limited to any specific school or style of magic. Choose your abilities and wage battle using powerful combinations of elemental spells! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/01970cd4a0b51082723f18d4a96fc535.poster.avif?t=1708977933\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/01970cd4a0b51082723f18d4a96fc535.webm?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/01970cd4a0b51082723f18d4a96fc535.mp4?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Choose</strong> abilities from any of the elements and switch things up to engage in tactical spellcasting battles.<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/91116482146c5b46bb725adcd4022e0a.poster.avif?t=1708977933\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/91116482146c5b46bb725adcd4022e0a.webm?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/91116482146c5b46bb725adcd4022e0a.mp4?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battlemages</strong> enter the training grounds via portals that connect worlds. Train your skills against others in elemental combat!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/c02b5b8ed3af1f1048baed6381296cd9.poster.avif?t=1708977933\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/c02b5b8ed3af1f1048baed6381296cd9.webm?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851840/extras/c02b5b8ed3af1f1048baed6381296cd9.mp4?t=1708977933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Master </strong>the elements: Fire, Frost, and Earth. Choose your abilities to match your playstyle, fit your team, and battle your opponents!<br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online arena combat<br></li><li>Offline horde mode<br></li><li>Choose any combination of Fire, Earth, and Ice magic<br></li><li>Health, mana, and stamina resources that can be attacked via different skills<br></li><li>Primary attacks have stacking buffs and debuffs</li></ul>",
